The Mindanao Geothermal Production Field also known as the Mount Apo Geothermal Power Plant is located in Barangay Ilomavis, Kidapawan City, North Cotabato Near Foot of Mount Apo with a power output of 106 MW, currently of Kind of Mindanao Grid to supplies electricity to Kidapawan and Davao Region.
Impounds: Mount Apo
Turbines: Dry Steam Power Plant 54.24 megawatts
